### ==========================================
### Lab 02: @Transactional(readOnly=true) 실제 효과
### ==========================================

### ------------------------------------------
### 실험 2-A: readOnly 상태 확인
### ------------------------------------------
### FlushMode, DefaultReadOnly 확인

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/experiments/readonly-status
Accept: application/json

### ------------------------------------------
### 실험 2-B: readOnly에서 persist 후 커밋 결과 검증
### ------------------------------------------
### persist 후 커밋 완료 → 별도 트랜잭션에서 재조회하여 DB 반영 여부 확인

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/experiments/readonly-modify
Accept: application/json

### ------------------------------------------
### 실험 2-C: readOnly 성능 비교
### ------------------------------------------
### readOnly=true vs false 성능 차이

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/experiments/readonly-performance
Accept: application/json

### ------------------------------------------
### 실험 2-D: readOnly에서 명시적 flush 동작 확인
### ------------------------------------------
### persist + 명시적 flush() 호출 후 커밋 → 재조회로 DB 반영 여부 확인

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/experiments/readonly-persist
Accept: application/json

### ------------------------------------------
### 🧪 모든 실험 한 번에 실행
### ------------------------------------------
### 콘솔 로그를 확인하세요!

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/experiments/all
Accept: application/json
